$grp PS_MissionDescription : "{3136BE42592F3B1B}PrefabsEditable/MissionDescription/EditableMissionDescription.et" {
 CS2 {
  coords 3985.968 0 11858.752
  m_sTitle "Comsig"
  m_sTextData "<h2>RADIO FREQ</h2>"\
  "• All callsigns: 38hz"\
  ""\
  "<h2>MISC</h2>"\
  "• <b>Challanege:</b> Mince | <b>Password:</b> Pie"\
  ""\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "ECO"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
 EN2 {
  coords 3994.177 0 11883.197
  m_sTitle "Enemy forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>"\
  "Our enemy is anyone who stands against real change on this earth."\
  "For far too long, nations have failed to act while the rich grow richer and the poor grow poorer. Now they will be forced to respond."\
  "In this moment, our immediate enemy will be the British state."\
  ""\
  "We can expect a rapid reaction to our presence, as our actions have already made it clear that this rig is under our control. The closest military unit is 42 Commando, stationed at the airfield north of our position, and they are the most likely force to respond."\
  "The scale and method of their assault are currently unknown."\
  ""\
  "Their staging location is the airfield at GRID: 048117."\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>"\
  "Unknown."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "ECO"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 FRN2 {
  coords 3990.274 0 11873.757
  m_sTitle "Friendly forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>"\
  "We are the Earth Contamination Outfit (ECO), a collection of radical environmentalists who believe real change will only come through direct action. Our goal is to force the world to confront ecological collapse by creating disasters that affect everyone — rich and poor alike — until nations abandon fossil fuels and transition to renewable energy."\
  ""\
  "Our ECO cell consists of 11 personnel."\
  "Our current location is the TEM POWER oil rig at GRID: 048017."\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>"\
  "We are limited in modern weaponry and equipment, but what we lack in technology we make up for with conviction, determination, and belief in our cause."\
  ""\
  "We are prepared to go down with this rig. Death before surrender."\
  "Our arsenal consists of a mix of modern, Cold War, and even WWII-era weapons, including rifles, machine guns, submachine guns, shotguns, and bolt-action rifles from both Western and Eastern origins."\
  ""\
  "Personnel are equipped with high explosive and smoke grenades. Most fighters carry at least one of each, with some carrying additional grenades."\
  "Our machine gunners carry heavier equipment and protective gear, making them slower but better protected."\
  ""\
  "All personnel are equipped with radios."\
  "We also possess zip-cuffs for restraining the captured hostages."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "ECO"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 MIS2 {
  coords 3994.644 0 11883.534
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "<h2>MISSION STATEMENT</h2>"\
  "Our mission is to DEFEND the oil rig for the next 35 minutes while the bomb counts down to detonation."\
  ""\
  "<h2>EXECUTION</h2>"\
  "<b>BOMB:</b>  "\
  "The bomb is currently armed and positioned on a pallet truck within the drilling compound, located on the ground floor at the center of the rig, at the base of the large tower."\
  ""\
  "If enemy forces manage to secure and hold this compound for too long, they will likely be able to defuse the device. This area must remain secured at all times."\
  ""\
  "<b>ENEMY TROOPS:</b>  "\
  "Our primary objective is not the destruction of enemy forces, but the defense of the bomb itself."\
  ""\
  "If the bomb is successfully defused, our focus should shift to eliminating enemy forces where possible in order to create an opportunity to withdraw and continue our operations elsewhere in the future."\
  ""\
  "<b>HOSTAGES:</b>  "\
  "Hostages may be positioned where we see fit, provided they are not used to physically block access points or exploited in unrealistic ways to gain cover or other unfair advantages."\
  ""\
  "That said, hostages may be used as a deterrent to discourage enemy fire directed at ourselves or the bomb area."\
  ""\
  "Hostages are only strategically useful while the bomb remains active, as they can delay or complicate enemy action. If the bomb is defused, they no longer serve a strategic purpose and may be dealt with at our discretion."\
  ""\
  "<b>(Hostage players have been instructed to generally comply with OPFOR orders. However, they may choose to attempt escape or disobey instructions at their own discretion, at which point their fate is in the hands of OPFOR.)</b>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "ECO"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 SIT2 {
  coords 3995.67 0 11888.938
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>PRELIMS</h2> "\
  "Date: 1st May 2020"\
  "Time: Random"\
  "Location: Mull of Kintyre, Scotland"\
  "Weather: Random"\
  ""\
  "<h2>LORE</h2> "\
  "Radical environmentalists from the Earth Contamination Outfit (ECO) have launched a surprise attack on a TEM POWER oil rig off the coast of Scotland."\
  ""\
  "British intelligence has been monitoring our movement for several years as our organization has grown more prominent across the UK. Despite this scrutiny, the planning and preparation for this operation — including the movement of weapons and equipment — managed to slip past their surveillance."\
  "Our group has conducted smaller operations throughout the country before, but nothing on this scale."\
  ""\
  "Arriving by boat, we ascended the access stairs and seized the rig by force. A number of crew members managed to escape using the lifeboats, but several were captured during the takeover."\
  "Five workers are now being held hostage. They will serve as leverage when the inevitable assault comes."\
  ""\
  "Today may be our final stand, but change will follow in our wake."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "ECO"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
}